data.description: Located in the heart of greenbrier, this beautiful home with gorgeous views of the water and Greenbrier country club golf course is ready for new owners! This home features a huge deck an updated kitchen, sunken den and cathedral ceilings. The primary bedroom offers a balcony to admire the views to the fullest, a large closet, and huge en-suite with jetted tub, separate shower, and double-sinks. This home leaves little to be desired!
